Title: 
Global Hotel Promotion Remind!

Body:
<table width="95%" height="300" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
  <tr>
    <td valign="top"><span class="textblack"><br>
      <br>
      </span>Dear ${x_user.name},
      <p>This is to remind you that you haven't responsed for your global hotel promotion yet, please respond.</p>
      <table width="90%" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="1" bgcolor="#666666">
        <tr bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
          <td align="center" class="bold"><div align="left">Hotel Name</div></td>
          <td align="center" class="bold"><div align="left">Hotel City</div></td>
          <td align="center" class="bold"><div align="left">Promote Message</div></td>
          
        #foreach( $hotel in $x_hotelList )      
        <tr bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
        	<td class="textblack">${hotel.name}</td>          
          <td class="textblack">${hotel.city.engName}</td>
          <td class="textblack">${hotel.promoteMessage}</td>
        </tr>
        #end
      </table>
      <p>Please use your web browser to go to:<br>
        ${visitUrl} visit our system.</p>
      <p>${regardWords}<br>
        ${signature}<br>
    </p></td>
  </tr>
</table>